          The CTG facility is optimized for striking, self defense, and small group training. It is not a generic event space. We prioritize programs that align with our focus on safety, empowerment, and practical skills.
        </p>

        <div class="grid two-col">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Facility Highlights</h3>
