              <li>Striking bags, pads, and training equipment</li>
              <li>Designated spectator or waiting area</li>
              <li>Convenient Chapel Hill location</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Space Use & Partnerships</h3>
